rted: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to his companions, \u201cIs it difficult for one of you to recite a third of the Quran in a single night?\u201d That was difficult for them, so they said, \u201cWhich one of us can do that, O\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3852,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/27\/surah-ikhlaas-third-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":37360,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Surat al-Ikhlas worth one-third of Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 27, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa'id al-Khudri reported: A man heard another man reciting, \"Say, He is Allah, the One,\" (112:1) again and again. The next morning he came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and told him about it, as if he thought it was not enough to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37568,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/waswas-salat\/","url_meta":{"origin":37360,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: How to repel the devil\u2019s whispering in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-\u2018Ala\u2019 reported: Uthman ibn al-\u2018As came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, Satan interferes between me, my prayer, and my recitation, confusing me.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cSuch is Satan, who is called rotten. When you sense him, then seek\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3876,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/28\/shaytan-runs-surah-baqarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37360,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Satan runs from Al-Baqarah recitation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDo not turn your houses into graveyards. Verily, Satan flees from the house in which Surat al-Baqarah is recited.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 780 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3087,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/28\/surah-al-fatihah-every-prayer\/","url_meta":{"origin":37360,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Recitation of Surat al-Fatihah in every prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is no prayer for one who does not recite the opening of the Book, Surat al-Fatihah.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 756, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 394 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37360","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=37360"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/37360\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=37360"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=37360"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=37360"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}